Using tags for both types of media and for activities or genre.


Functionality:
    genres are overlapping. So even though horror is primarly marked as a movie/book genre it can be added to other genres as well.




Tagsfield: 
    Functionality:
        Inputfield where you add tags for the book you are adding.
        These tags are then added to an array stored in the book object.
        Pressing enter while having the field selected should add the tag